                                              "is_correct":  false,
                                              "feedback":  "Opportunity cost is central to comparative advantage."
                                          },
                                          {
                                              "id":  "D",
                                              "text":  "Because each country can focus on goods it produces at lower opportunity cost",
                                              "is_correct":  true,
                                              "feedback":  "Correct. Comparative advantage shows that specialization and trade can improve efficiency."
                                          }
